Raleigh the Devout
Go to the village and talk to my friend, he will tell you what to do. He lives in the house with the blue roof.
Your trials with me are finished... here in the Valley. But I want you to report your findings. Go to the village and seek out Master Gadrin. The village is east out of the valley. Tell Gadrin of what we did. Go, #, and be swift. I fear the evil we found is but the herald of a larger threat...
